data.description: Active Under Contract - Accepting Back Up Offers. This beautiful two bed, two bath home with a POOL, New Roof 10/2022 and New HVAC 2/2021 is located in the desirable Spring Hill neighborhood. This home offers 1408 square feet of living space and features a two-car attached garage, a sparkling new diamond bright pool, new pool heater, and Jacuzzi/hot tub. The backyard is fully fenced and perfect for entertaining.Inside, you will find tile floors throughout, a skylight for more amazing natural light, and an indoor laundry room with a separate door leading out to the garage. The kitchen is equipped with plenty of storage, counter space, and overlooks the sparkling swimming pool. The living room is bright and inviting. The bedrooms are spacious and comfortable.This home is the perfect place to relax and enjoy the Florida sunshine. With its convenient location, close proximity to shopping, dining, and entertainment, and its many amenities, this home is sure to please. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a piece of paradise.
